query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS fx_rates (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  date DATE NOT NULL,
  rateUsd DECIMAL(12,4) NOT NULL,
  regimeTag ENUM('IRG', 'DFA', 'PAR') NOT NULL,
  sourceId INT NOT NULL,
  ingestionRunId INT NULL,
  vintageDate DATE NULL,
  retrievalDate DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  rawFileS3Path VARCHAR(500) NULL,
  confidenceRating ENUM('A', 'B', 'C', 'D') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'B',
  isInterpolated BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT FALSE,
  notes TEXT NULL,
  labelEn VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  labelAr VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  createdAt DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  updatedAt DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  UNIQUE KEY unique_date_regime (date, regimeTag),
  INDEX idx_regime_date (regimeTag, date),
  INDEX idx_date (date)
);
